cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IT, cs.MM

This paper is about deep learning-based medical image registration, which involves computer vision (CV) and machine learning (ML) techniques. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also proposes a novel deep learning framework that combines affine and non-parametric registration methods, which involves optimization and learning techniques. Therefore, cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) are also likely sub-categories. The paper also involves mathematical modeling and signal processing techniques, which are related to information theory (cs.IT) and multimedia (cs.MM).
